title: The Christmas Secret aka Flight of the Reindeer 2000 CBS-Hallmar
description:
The Christmas Secret
a.k.a Flight of the Reindeer



If reindeer can fly then anything is possible. Finally after years of being scoffed at by friends and colleagues Jerry McNeal has secured documented proof that reindeer can fly. In fact not only does he have photgraphs and videotape of reindeer flying he has also found the magical North Pole village where they live with St. Nick and the elves.

Based on the speculative book "Flight of the Reindeer" written by Robert Sullivan.
